Sant Joan d'Alacant, with a population of 19 711 in 2005, is a small
municipality belonging to Alicante metropolitan area, in the south
east of the Valencian Community in Spain
(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sant_Joan_d%27Alacant); Sant Joan
d'Alacant is reported to be a non-tourist, bedroom community for
Alicante. The Valencian Community is one of 17 autonomous communities
in Spain and is located along the central Mediterranean coastline of
Spain (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alcasser). The
HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Spain can be accessed at
http://healthmap.org/r/14-l. - Mod.ML]
